	</div>
	<div class="container content">
		<h2>I am a freelance web designer and front-end developer living and working in Richmond, B.C., Canada.</h2>
		<div class="wrapper aboutMe">
			<h3>I specialize in HTML5, CSS3, Javascript, and Jquery... but I am always learning more. Two other technologies I have started to learn are Ajax and Node.js, as well as dabbling in PHP. I am currently searching for small-business and personal opportunites for both work and self improvement. <br><p>I look forward to talking to you soon.</p> <br> :) </h3>
